comments: Bjelica (SAC) makes contact with Markkanen (CHI) that affects his shot attempt at the basket.
Holmes (SAC) makes marginal contact with LaVine (CHI) when he sets the screen.
Dunn (CHI) makes contact with Hield (SAC) that affects his SQBR.
Bogdanovic (SAC) releases from contact with LaVine (CHI) at the end of his drive to the basket.
Carter Jr. (CHI) makes contact to Holmes's (SAC) arm as he attempts the putback shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in Hield's (SAC) path and does not deliver contact during the pick.
LaVine (CHI) establishes himself in Bogdanovic's (SAC) path and does not deliver contact during the pick.
Barnes (SAC) makes marginal contact with Dunn (CHI) as he firms up while setting the pick.
Carter Jr. (CHI) makes contact with Hield's (SAC) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Joseph (SAC) places a hand/arm to the front of LaVine (CHI) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Barnes (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball as Carter Jr. (CHI) attempts to secure the pass.
Dunn (CHI) makes brief arm contact with Ferrell (SAC) but does not affect his SQBR.
Carter Jr. (CHI) makes marginal arm contact with Ferrell (SAC) but does not affect his ability to release the pass.
Joseph (SAC) makes marginal contact with LaVine (CHI) during the pass.
Ferrell (SAC) commits a take foul on Satoransky (CHI).
Ferrell (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Dunn (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Carter Jr. (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Markkanen (CHI) commits a loose ball foul on Barnes (SAC).
Ferrell (SAC) commits a take foul on LaVine (CHI).
Carter Jr. (CHI) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Barnes' (SAC) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Markkanen (CHI) makes marginal contact with Holmes (SAC) during the rebound.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on LaVine (CHI).
